ðŸ›  Troubleshooting
1. Camera Not Detected

    Symptom: /dev/video* devices are missing.

    Solution: Manually load the driver modules or restart the relay service.
    Bash

    sudo modprobe v4l2loopback
    sudo systemctl restart v4l2-relayd

2. High Latency Issues

    Symptom: Significant lag during real-time tracking.

    Solution: Expand the network kernel receive buffer.
    Bash

    sudo sysctl -w net.core.rmem_max=2147483647

3. Permission Errors

    Solution: Ensure your user is part of the video and render groups.
    Bash

sudo usermod -aG video,render $USER
